column1: # measurement units, case insensitive so everything is lower case for simplicity
# the comments after // are required by UnitNormalizer for unit normalization! Do not remove
# note: multi-word phrases must be tokenized in the same way as our tokenizer. If not sure, try the phrases in ./shell first!
ton for one hectare  // t/ha::areal density
metric ton per hectare     // t/ha::areal density
metric tons per hectare    // t/ha::areal density
mole per cubic meter       // mol/m3::amount-of-substance concentration
cubic meter per hour       // m3/h::volumetric flow
